    </div>
    <div class="fragment">
      <h6 class="InfoHeader InfoHeader--tight">Composable</h6>
      <p class="InfoParagraph">Use Ember Modal Dialog components in your own components or addons</p>
    </div>
    <div class="fragment">
      <h6 class="InfoHeader InfoHeader--tight">Flexible</h6>
      <p class="InfoParagraph">Toggle between different modal components or positioning strategies</p>
    </div>

    {{#reveal-slide-notes}}
      - Avoids a lot of boilerplate code
      - Framework manages life cycle for you
      - Building blocks for your own components, apps, addons
      - Component helper to select different implementations, render the component in place in style guides, etc.
    {{/reveal-slide-notes}}
  {{/reveal-slide}}

