    {{#reveal-slide-notes}}
      - `ember-modal-dialog` initializer appends modal container `#modalRootElementId` to the Ember app root element
      - `modal-dialog` component composes with `ember-wormhole`
      - `ember-wormhole` moves and removes your modal content over the course of its life cycle
      - Resultant DOM is similar to that of the old named outlet approach
    {{/reveal-slide-notes}}
